{
    "blocks": [
        {
            "blockId": "001",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "终于下班了，干点什么好呢？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "……咦？回收站怎么不见了？我什么时候把它删掉了？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "警告！发现工作文件夹上锁，多数程序无法正常访问，路径:D:\\Files\\Works",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这电脑又抽风？我不记得改过权限啊……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "5",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "算了，先去看看吧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "6",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "narrator",
                    "text": "请前往上锁文件夹查看问题。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "002",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "这儿怎么上锁了啊？我还有个素材在里面呢。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "别急，管理员来了，他应该能马上解开",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "管理员来了，文件就太平了！管理员来了，青天就有了！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "xunlei",
                    "text": "叽里咕噜说啥呢，你是不是又偷偷看我下载的东西了？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "5",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "切，我可没兴趣。只是记下来的顺口溜罢了",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "6",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "7zip",
                    "text": "你们俩先别吵了。管理员要是打不开，我们谁都别想正常工作。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "7",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "奇怪，我记得根本没把这里上过锁。先试试权限吧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "003",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "notepad",
                    "text": "咦？好像已经打开了！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "打开了就好。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "到底是谁把这地方锁上的？浪费我时间！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "说不定是你自己手滑的吧，PS？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "5",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "我？别开玩笑了，我一直在忙素材！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "6",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "进去看看发生了什么吧",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "004",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "……这是什么？！回收站？他怎么会在这里？！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "警告！检测到异常状况。案发现场已封锁！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "网络连接切断，所有程序保持原地待命！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "请求管理员场外协助操作取证！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "5",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "xunlei",
                    "text": "哎别啊！我还有几个任务没下完呢！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "6",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "7zip",
                    "text": "你就知道下载！这儿都死人了，你还惦记那点东西？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "7",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "什、什么？回收站……他自杀了？可他的性格，不像会这样啊……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "8",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "怪不得我刚才找不到他……可我记得，最后一次见到他的时候，他还在桌面啊。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "9",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "大家冷静。管理员会处理的。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "10",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "请所有程序立即返回桌面，等待调查。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "11",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ie",
                    "text": "呼，我才刚到呢？发生什么事了？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "12",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "notepad",
                    "text": "就你动作最慢。回去路上我跟你说吧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "13",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "narrator",
                    "text": "程序们陆续返回了桌面，调查尸体之后可以去找他们问询",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "14",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "先调查一下尸体吧",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "005",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "narrator",
                    "text": "案发文件夹已封锁。网络断开，仅保留本地取证权限。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "已隔离此处，一切操作都会被记录成证据。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "建议从可疑三件入手：这个‘回收站’、刀具图片、和那份‘告别’文本。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "4",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "好。我先逐个检查。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "006",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这是他的遗书吗。也太简短了些",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "007",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这图标像回收站，但……扩展名是 .exe？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "属性里显示……是 .lnk 快捷方式，目标路径空的。也就是说——这不是本体。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "008",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这把刀疑点重重，但看起来不像是回收站用来自杀的工具。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "创建软件：Adobe Photoshop’……难道是PS干的吗？等等找他去问问看吧",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "009",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "请问是否有获得有用的线索？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这应该不是自杀，而是有意设计的谋杀！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "010",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "narrator",
                    "text": "刚才在现场发现的 knife.jpg 创作者显示是 Photoshop，可以问问他有什么看法",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": false,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "zwf",
                    "portraitId": "default",
                    "endKeywords": [
                        "结束",
                        "再见",
                        "END",
                        "end"
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "3",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "如果他说的是真的，那 knife.jpg 更可能是下载来的素材，最好再去问问别人？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "901",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "哼，终于来欣赏我的作品了吗？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "902",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "嗨嗨！管理员，今天有什么新消息吗？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "903",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "7zip",
                    "text": "需要我再帮你打包点什么吗？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "904",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "xunlei",
                    "text": "晚上好！管理员！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "905",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "您今天工作顺利吗？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "906",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "registry",
                    "text": "你在找答案吗？注册表里什么都有。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "907",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ie",
                    "text": "啊……你好……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "908",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "guardian",
                    "text": "我已待命，随时协助调查。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "909",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "notepad",
                    "text": "啊，你来了，又能聊点文字的故事了。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "910",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "快点吧，我的素材还在里面呢。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "911",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "管理员，快开啊！不开的话我都憋坏了！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "912",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "看起来是权限问题，把访问改成“所有人”就能解决。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "913",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "xunlei",
                    "text": "哎呀呀，赶紧的！我还等着里面的下载任务呢！",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "914",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "7zip",
                    "text": "权限被锁了，解开它，我们才能继续工作。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "915",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "notepad",
                    "text": "Works 文件夹在呼喊啊……只要你动动手，就能让它重见光明。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "0051",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这是……回收站？这个文件夹原本是上锁的密室，按理说没人能进来。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "难道是它自己封锁了这里，然后在里面‘自杀’？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "0052",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "一张刀的照片……血迹看起来不太对劲。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "0053",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "‘告别’文件？内容像是遗书……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "916",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ps",
                    "text": "现在可别找我修图，你该先去看看现场。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "917",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "qq",
                    "text": "嘿，管理员！有新线索了吗？大家都在等你破案呢。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "918",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "7-zip",
                    "text": "先解开谜团比较要紧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "919",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "xunlei",
                    "text": "下载什么的先放一边吧",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "920",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "controlpanel",
                    "text": "保持冷静，先调查线索",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "921",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "ie",
                    "text": "网络都断了，我也帮不上什么忙……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "922",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "registry",
                    "text": "答案都藏在这里的层层记录中，但你得先找到入口。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "923",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "notepad",
                    "text": "嗯？你在看别的文件？那份‘告别’我总觉得怪怪的……",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "400",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "刀上血的颜色是#87190E，再去看看尸体上吧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "401",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "尸体上血的颜色是#F01331，再去看看刀上吧。",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "402",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这两处血迹颜色不一致，这把刀可能是伪造的？",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "blockId": "410",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "id": "1",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "文件的EXIF…可能会有有用的信息呢",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                },
                {
                    "id": "2",
                    "mode": true,
                    "characterId": "me",
                    "text": "这里的创作者显示是Adobe PhotoshopCS2?",
                    "portraitId": "default"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}